description: Dean Tucker has proven himself as one of the most skilled fighters here. He’s fought in oil, water, mud, and in front of an audience and still managed to tack up a record of 3-1. An imposing opponent for the newcomer Tristan Jaxx, who brings a street fighting background along with his huge uncut cock. Can Tristan overcome the curse of the NK first-timers and claim a victory or will the expertise of Dean hold on strong?
title: Dean Tucker vs Tristan Jaxx
